'''丹尼爾·希恩'''（{{lang-en|Daniel P. Sheehan}}，{{bd|1945年|4月9日||}}）是[[美國|美國]]憲法和公眾利益[[律師|律師]]。

== 生平 ==
希恩畢業於[[哈佛法學院|哈佛法學院]]。在他40年的律師職業生涯中曾參與了許多重大歷史案件的法律訴訟歷程，包括[[紐約時報訴美國案|五角大厦文件案]]和[[水門案|水門案]]等<ref>{{Cite web|title=Hollywood comes calling for Daniel Sheehan|url=https://www.mercurynews.com/2013/09/19/hollywood-comes-calling-for-daniel-sheehan/|accessdate=2021-01-07|date=2013-09-19|work=The Mercury News|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191112000342/https://www.mercurynews.com/2013/09/19/hollywood-comes-calling-for-daniel-sheehan/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Santa Cruz’s Connection to 'The Post'|url=https://goodtimes.sc/santa-cruz-news/santa-cruzs-connection-the-post/|accessdate=2021-01-07|date=2018-02-21|last=Johnson|first=Georgia|work=Good Times Santa Cruz|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930221606/https://goodtimes.sc/santa-cruz-news/santa-cruzs-connection-the-post/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1976年，希恩擔任[[國會研究處|國會研究處]]科學與技術分析師[[瑪西婭·史密斯|瑪西婭·史密斯]]（Marcia Smith）的顧問<ref>{{Cite web|title=UFO findings kept a secret|url=https://www.columbiatribune.com/article/20101221/News/312219703|accessdate=2021-01-07|date=2010-12-21|last=WICKERSHAM|first=BILL|publisher=Columbia Daily Tribune|language=en|archive-date=2019-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190815213235/https://www.columbiatribune.com/article/20101221/News/312219703|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1980年他創立了公益律師事務所{{le|克里斯蒂研究所|Christic Institute}}，並擔任總法律顧問和調查主任<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/opinions/1988/09/11/the-ultimate-conspiracy-theory/4fb678ce-2ff6-4c80-ad7f-9f63bb9a328e/|title=The Ultimate Conspiracy Theory|date=1988-09-11|work=Washington Post|accessdate=2021-01-08|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210122053616/https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/opinions/1988/09/11/the-ultimate-conspiracy-theory/4fb678ce-2ff6-4c80-ad7f-9f63bb9a328e/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該組織目前由{{le|羅梅羅研究所|Romero Institute}}延續。

長期以來，希恩對[[不明飛行物|不明飛行物]]現象一直感興趣<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Ex-official who revealed UFO project accuses Pentagon of 'disinformation' campaign|url=https://www.politico.com/news/2021/05/26/ufo-whistleblower-ig-complaint-pentagon-491098|access-date=2021-06-26|date=2021-05-26|last=Bender|first=Bryan|work=POLITICO|language=en|archive-date=2021-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210709105320/https://www.politico.com/news/2021/05/26/ufo-whistleblower-ig-complaint-pentagon-491098}}</ref>。他參與了[[幽浮學|幽浮學]]家[[史蒂芬·格里爾|史蒂芬·格里爾]]領導的「[[揭秘计划|揭秘计划]]」，擔任總法律顧問<ref>{{cite news|title=Group Calls for Disclosure of UFO Info|url=https://abcnews.go.com/Technology/story?id=98572&page=1|accessdate=2021-01-07|publisher=ABC News|date=2001-05-10|archive-date=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131050852/https://abcnews.go.com/Technology/story?id=98572&page=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。希恩還是不明飛行物[[舉報人|舉報人]]、[[美國國防部|國防部]]{{le|高等航太威脅辨識計畫|Advanced Aerospace Threat Identification Program}}前負責人{{le|路易斯·艾利桑多|Luis Elizondo}}的律師<ref name=":0" />。

